<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-77-1017 </DOCNO><TEXT>This article deals with the preliminary results af a census on water depurationplants, that was carried out last year by UIDA. Among the several findings,the fact emerges that existing plants serve 40% of the population andthat about half of these are either not functioning, or functioning improperly.</TEXT></DOC>